Mith my bard friend we desided to check out keal and se how the exp was. It was pretty good post POP.<br>
<br>
What we did was we headed to bank area where most giants are blue. I summoned my earth pet (root). My job as the higher lvl one was to pull with malosie or who ever it is spelled and just chain summone earth pets. The pets can tank pretty good and with ds they do pretty nice dmg too. The bard just used all the dots he had and they went down nice and easy. With KEI I we never had to stop and if we got and add I had a charmer next to me. U could do this solo but it is much faster and safer with a bard. If u desides that the add was to much run towards the ent and jump down the small ledge the giants will run around it and u will have plenty of time to gate or summon new pet.<br>
